            <h3 id="contact-information">Contact Information</h3>
            <p>If you have any questions about the database, or suggestions for improving it, please get in touch. We welcome feedback from researchers, students, practitioners, and anyone with an interest in construction management research; including anyone involved in cataloguing, indexing, or managing similar databases in other topic areas.</p>
            <p>These explanatory notes and commentaries have been written by Prof Will Hughes as the curator of the site and reflect personal understanding and interpretation. They are offered to clarify the structure and intent of the catalogue and to encourage thoughtful discussion.</p>
